Commands
Weather
  weather — Current conditions for a location.
  alerts — Active weather alerts for a location.
  sun — Sunrise and sunset times for a location.
  wind — Current wind speed and direction.
  next-cloudy — The next cloudy day in the forecast window.
  uv — Current + max UV and sunscreen window for a location.
Forecast
  weekday-forecast — Multi-day weekday (Mon-Fri) forecast.
  weekend-forecast — Multi-day weekend (Fri-Sat-Sun) forecast.
Info
  help — List all available commands.
  locations — List the configured locations.
  status — Daemon liveness and next scheduled sends.
